No. 35,

Orig.

United States v. Maine et al. [For earlier decision herein, see, e. g., 452 U. S. 429.]

Report of the Special Master on the Rhode Island boundary is received and ordered filed. Exceptions to the Report, with supporting briefs, may be filed by the parties within 45 days. Replies to such Exceptions, with supporting briefs, may be filed within 30 days.
